B.aQh=new A.cF(10,"Critical development phase is nearly complete! Fingernails are forming.","Vital organs are in place. Baby is now classified as a fetus.")
B.b4P=s(["Nausea starting to ease","Increased energy","Mild heartburn"],t.s)
B.aQl=new A.cF(11,"Tooth buds are forming. Baby can open and close fists.","External genitalia beginning to differentiate. Skin is see-through.")
B.b4O=s(["Morning sickness often eases","Increased appetite returning","Visible bump starting"],t.s)
B.aQG=new A.cF(12,"All organs, muscles, limbs and bones are in place. Unique fingerprints have formed!","Baby's reflexes are developing \u2014 toes curl, fingers open and close.")
B.b4x=s(["Energy boost","Reduced nausea","Visible veins on abdomen","Mild back pain"],t.s)
B.aQu=new A.cF(13,"Baby can make facial expressions and vocal cords are developing.","Intestines move from umbilical cord into abdomen. Tissue becomes bone.")
B.b4V=s(["Increased appetite","Skin changes (glow!)","Reduced fatigue","Slight weight gain"],t.s)
B.aQs=new A.cF(14,"Face looks recognizable. Kidneys are producing urine into amniotic fluid.","Baby's red blood cells are being produced by the spleen.")
B.b4Q=s(["Round ligament pain","Nasal congestion","Increased sex drive possible"],t.s)
B.aQF=new A.cF(15,"Baby can sense light through closed eyelids. Skeleton hardening from cartilage to bone.","Ears are in final position. Baby may be moving though you can't feel it yet.")
B.b4s=s(["Growing bump","Back pain","Possible constipation","Skin darkening (linea nigra)"],t.s)
B.aQz=new A.cF(16,"Baby can hear your voice! Facial muscles allow expressions.","Baby making swallowing movements. Amniotic fluid is swallowed and recycled.")
B.b4k=s(["Stretch marks may appear","Increased appetite","Itchy skin on belly"],t.s)
B.aQA=new A.cF(17,"Fat stores beginning to develop. Sweat glands forming.","Skeleton changing from cartilage to bone rapidly.")
B.b4l=s(["Baby flutters (quickening) may begin","Lower back pain","Mild swelling in ankles"],t.s)
B.aQ8=new A.cF(18,"Ears are fully positioned. Baby can yawn and hiccup!","Nerves forming a protective myelin sheath. All senses are developing.")
B.b4z=s(["Baby kicks & flutters!","Growing appetite","Dizziness when standing quickly"],t.s)
B.aQm=new A.cF(19,"First movements (quickening) often felt this week! Vernix (protective coating) forming.","Brain is designating specialized areas for all 5 senses.")
B.b4v=s(["Braxton Hicks contractions starting","Heartburn","Swollen feet","Hip pain"],t.s)
B.aQf=new A.cF(20,"\ud83c\udf89 Halfway there! Eyebrows, eyelashes and fingernails are fully formed.","Baby is more active, around 16cm long. Hair growing on the head.")
B.b4p=s(["Visible kicks from outside!","Increased backache","Stretch marks","Leg cramps"],t.s)
B.aQg=new A.cF(21,"Baby can taste what you eat through amniotic fluid.","Bone marrow beginning to make blood cells. Liver and spleen helping too.")
B.b4r=s(["Linea nigra darkening","Innie belly button becoming an outie","Heartburn"],t.s)
B.aQi=new A.cF(22,"Sleep-wake cycles forming. Face is fully formed with eyebrows and lips.","Tear ducts are developing. Grip reflex is strong.")
B.b4u=s(["Braxton Hicks contractions","Swelling (edema)","Increased pigmentation"],t.s)
B.aQj=new A.cF(23,"Sense of movement is developing. Lungs are preparing for breathing.","Skin is still wrinkled \u2014 baby will fill it out with fat over coming weeks.")
B.b4L=s(["Shortness of breath","Backache","Swollen feet and ankles","Carpal tunnel tingling"],t.s)
B.aQy=new A.cF(24,"Survival possible if born now! Baby responds clearly to sound and touch.","Lungs developing surfactant \u2014 the substance that allows breathing after birth.")
B.b4m=s(["Sciatica (shooting pain down leg)","Swelling","Hemorrhoids may appear"],t.s)
B.aQa=new A.cF(25,"Baby is adding fat stores and growing more hair.","Capillaries forming under skin \u2014 baby's skin turning pink.")
B.b4B=s(["Insomnia","Painful Braxton Hicks","Frequent urination returns","Vivid dreams"],t.s)
B.aQk=new A.cF(26,"\ud83d\udc41\ufe0f Baby's eyes can open for the first time! Lungs developing surfactant.","Brain wave activity for hearing and sight detected. Inhaling amniotic fluid.")
B.b4T=s(["Heartburn","Hemorrhoids","Leg cramps at night","Lower back pain"],t.s)
B.aQn=new A.cF(27,"Brain is very active. Baby may get hiccups you can feel!","Last week of the 2nd trimester. Baby sleeping 90% of the time.")
B.b4D=s(["Shortness of breath","Vivid dreams","Discomfort sleeping","Pelvic pressure"],t.s)
B.aQx=new A.cF(28,"Eyes open and close with light sensitivity. REM sleep begins \u2014 baby may dream!","Brain growing at an incredible rate. Bones fully developed but soft.")
B.b4i=s(["Frequent urination","Pelvic girdle pain","Backache","Constipation"],t.s)
B.aQt=new A.cF(29,"Muscles and lungs maturing. Baby's head may be moving into head-down position.","Baby gaining about 200g per week from now until birth.")
B.b4y=s(["Heartburn","Nesting urge beginning","Swollen hands and face possible"],t.s)
B.aQc=new A.cF(30,"Bone marrow fully taking over red blood cell production. Toenails fully grown.","Baby's lanugo (soft hair) beginning to disappear. Fat accumulating fast.")
B.b4N=s(["Leaky colostrum from nipples","Breathlessness","More frequent Braxton Hicks"],t.s)
B.aQE=new A.cF(31,"All major fetal development is complete! Rapid weight gain phase begins.","Baby can turn head, suck thumb. Moving often and hard \u2014 you'll feel it!")
B.b4n=s(["Nesting instinct strong","Pelvic pressure","Diastasis recti","Trouble sleeping"],t.s)
B.aQ9=new A.cF(32,"Baby's practice breathing movements are regular. Toenails fully formed.","Skull remains flexible with soft spots (fontanelles) for passing through birth canal.")
B.b4g=s(["Difficulty breathing","Insomnia","Swollen face and hands","Lightning crotch pains"],t.s)
B.aQC=new A.cF(33,"Immune system building with antibodies from you. Skull is hardening (except fontanelles).","Baby's pupils can dilate and contract in response to light.")
B.b4M=s(["Pelvic pressure intensifies","Frequent urination","Back pain","Fatigue returns"],t.s)
B.aQd=new A.cF(34,"Central nervous system and lungs nearly mature. Baby settling head-down.","Vernix (protective coating) thickening. Fingernails now reach fingertips.")
B.b4t=s(["Braxton Hicks more intense","Difficulty walking","Pelvic lightening pain"],t.s)
B.aQr=new A.cF(35,"Kidneys are fully developed. Brain is only \u2154 of final weight \u2014 critical growth continues.","Baby is gaining half a pound per week now. Most internal organs fully ready.")
B.b4o=s(["Easier breathing after baby drops","Increased pelvic pressure","More frequent urination"],t.s)
B.aQB=new A.cF(36,'Baby may "drop" into the pelvis (lightening). Almost ready to be born!',"Baby's gums are rigid \u2014 ready for feeding. Skull plates still malleable.")
B.b4A=s(["Strong Braxton Hicks","Cervical changes","Mucus plug may pass","Nesting peaks"],t.s)
B.aQe=new A.cF(37,"Early full-term! All body systems are ready for life outside the womb.","Baby swallowing amniotic fluid \u2014 practising digestion. Meconium collecting.")
B.b4K=s(["Intense pelvic pressure","Back labor pain","Diarrhea (sign of labor approaching)","Difficulty sleeping"],t.s)
B.aQw=new A.cF(38,"Lungs and brain are fully mature. Baby is mostly sleeping and conserving energy.","Amniotic fluid decreasing as baby fills the space. Vernix coming off.")
B.b4S=s(["Contractions (true or Braxton Hicks)","Extreme fatigue","Emotional nesting","Mucus plug loss"],t.s)
